WITH

		SourceSystemid,
		PifSymbol,
		PifPolicyNumber,
		PifModule,
		PMDNXI1SegmentId,
		PMDNXI1SegmentStatus,
		PMDNXI1YearTransaction,
		PMDNXI1MonthTransaction,
		PMDNXI1DayTransaction,
		PMDNXI1SegmentLevelCode,
		PMDNXI1SegmentPartCode,
		PMDNXI1SubPartCode,

		PMDNXI1SubLocationNumber,

),
EXP_Pif43NXIMStage AS (

	ExtractDate,
	SourceSystemid,
	PifSymbol,

	PMDNXI1MonthTransaction,
	PMDNXI1DayTransaction,
	PMDNXI1SegmentLevelCode,

	PMDNXI1SubPartCode,

ArchPif43NXIMStage AS (

	PMDNXI1TRANSRADIUS, 
	PMDNXI1BUSINESSCLASS, 
	PMDNXI1TRANSGROUPN, 
	PMDNXI1EDPBACKUP, 
	PMDNXI1EDPADDLFACT, 
	PMDNXI1TRANSIND, 
	PMDNXI1EDPEQIND, 
	PMDNXI1PMSFUTUREUSE, 
	PMDNXI1MINIMUMPREMIUM,
